# rbtr search-quality benchmark

Hit@k / MRR / NDCG@10 for queries against the rbtr index. See
`packages/rbtr-eval/README.md` for methodology.

## Run

Reproduce: `cd packages/rbtr-eval && uv run dvc repro`.

